{"tid":1451211,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警犯罪資料庫","createTime":"2019-08-11T18:32:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T02:36:53.000Z","uid":113293,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fec7586fb8d778950770db5534c31abf41a9e078","tid":1451211,"uid":113293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:32:27.000Z","msg":"有冇手足一齊整個黑警犯罪資料庫？<br />\n<br />\n依家黑警越黎越瘋狂 我地要記錄所以黑警嘅罪證 寫個website 放上網。 到成功爭取獨立調查委員會之日 一一找出黑警 以為義士討回公道。<br />\n<br />\n但係班仆街每日都犯咁多法，真係要有人手去調查同記錄。有冇手足可以幫手成立team人去攪？"},{"pid":"7e9ab0a77e3bb22d33dabab73f59dec5b6ddde56","tid":1451211,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:34:35.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"5a95354a06618abe97b17f5c48a3bf1c84243f35","tid":1451211,"uid":113293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:37:54.000Z","msg":"我可以寫個website同db 但有冇手足幫手整理資料同簡單調查一下，如fact check, 警員編號，時間地點 之類？"},{"pid":"1c644e1fbe4bdf0c4d8741a60af62b58c38cfbdd","tid":1451211,"uid":113293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:43:11.000Z","msg":"召喚黑警調查員 請留tg"},{"pid":"eeea74556cd82097b16e99154f0f5eb5d36dfd77","tid":1451211,"uid":113293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:49:22.000Z","msg":"可以pm TG 我地一齊記錄黑警惡行 終有一日可以要黑警找數。<br />\n<br />\n個website可以公開 以後有藍絲命話示威者暴力 可以叫佢睇完先講野"},{"pid":"ef9c6763c62953e3d8fda5b87a47148bb282fa6b","tid":1451211,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:52:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黑警暴行</span></ins></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f7LDG8K.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff7LDG8K.gif&h=fcf92acc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/srfwh